<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of the sons of Korah.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, you have showed favor to your land;</para>

<para style="q1">you have restored the well-being of Jacob.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />You have forgiven the sin of your people;</para>

<para style="q1">you have covered all their sin.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
